vacancy.VacancyBigDescription:
Job Description

Working in GrabCAD you will be:
- Responsible for great user experience for industry leaders like NASA, Airbus, F1, BMW, Adidas
- Designing and developing innovative solutions for 3D printers
- Develop desktop applications using web technologies
- Writing automated tests to ensure your code works
- Deploying your own code to production
- Responsible for product quality
- Working with modern stack React, AngularJS, NodeJS, Electron, C#, Redis,
Ruby on Rails, PostgreSQL, Chef and AWS Stack

Requirements

We expect you to have:
- 3+ years experience in software development
- Willingness to work on all aspects up and down the dev stack
- Experience in using some of the following technologies: React, AngularJS, NodeJS, Electron, Redis, Ruby on Rails, PostgreSQL, Chef and AWS Stack
- Ability to learn new skills and languages
- Desire to work with bright minds
- Opinions and ideas

Company offers

- Get to know the latest 3D printing solutions
- Lots of 3D printers for development and personal usage
- Possibility to participate in work-related conferences

Modern technologies and ways of working:
- Our stack: React, Angular, NodeJS, Electron, C#, Rails, PostgreSQL, Redis
- CI – Chef, Berkshelf, Terraform, Jenkins, TeamCity
- Our environments are running on AWS
- Our developers also own product quality
- One-Click deployment
- We use Scrum

Friendly and inspiring environment
- Open-space office in the city center at Rotermanni Kvartal
- Fun team-building events and daily foosball matches
- Fridge stocked with chilled brews, snacks, fruits
- Competitive salary
- International working experience
- Cross-site teams in Estonia, UK, USA, Israel
- A team of highly skilled developers
- Opportunity to learn and grow in different areas

* Разработка и сопровождение систем (на базе MS SQL Server);
* Работа с хранилищами данных, отчетность, самописные и приобретенные продукты;
Интеграция с внешними и внутренними системами.
Обязателен опыт работы с:
* Microsoft SQL Server, T-SQL. (От 3-х лет)
* Microsoft SQL Server Reporting Services (От 1 года)
* ETL, DWH, OLAP, Bl (От года)
* Delphi (Клиентские приложения, Сервисы, Многопоточность, Интеграционные решения) (От 3-х лет)
* Навыки использования CVS (От года)
* Высшее техническое образование обязательно!
